value.0: Well, me and my pa... his name's Gerrol, everyone in Highcliff knows him... we live on a farm there.
There's lots of monsters that live in the hills around the High Road. Normally they don't bother us so much, but lately they've been ambushing travelers and caravans and such, being real bold.
They even went and kidnapped my mother while me and pa were away from the farm last week! So my pa sent me to look for help.
Pa says he's sent lots of messages about the troubles, but the mayor's all caught up fending off attacks from the swamp he's got no time to help us.
That would be great, my <lord/lady>. I'm sure my pa would appreciate it. To get to our farm, you just need to go south until you hit Highcliff and find him.
Umm... no. Should I have? I'm away from town a lot, so we don't get much news, I'm afraid.
We'd heard that a bunch of adventurers had come out of Neverwinter, however, so my pa sent me here to find some people to send to him. It's real important!
You just need to go South to Highcliff to speak to my pa in town, my <lord/lady>. I'll go back there when my pa calls me.
